weather - with Paris under thick cloud and occasional rain - also risked dampening the party.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1309, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.823815606175923e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"As well as the rail attacks\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"poor weather\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"thick cloud\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"occasional rain\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"the party\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will see tonight\\u2026 but the closer it gets the more the models suggest we are likely to get rain,\\\" chief Games organiser Tony Estanguet told France Inter radio, while adding that there would be some modifications if it was wet.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France Inter\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the models\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"rain\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1487}, {\"ngram\": \"some modifications\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's going to be a beautiful moment, it's going to be a